node.text:
Your language to the universe is frequency! The word consciousness is thrown about so casually that it’s easy to lose sight of what it means, even more so when it is defined as being “awakened.” Awakened consciousness is a state of being aware that you are aware. It is a realization that you are the watcher, the witness within you—not the analyzer, not the thinker, not even the meditator, but that which is the impartial witness of every aspect of your being and doing. 

Follow @MichaelbBeckwith for more!

node.title: Follow @MichaelbBeckwith for more wisdom on the law of attraction!✨

node.text: Here are 5 tips to follow when moving out for the first time.

node.accessibility_caption: Photo by Positive & Motivational Quotes on July 27, 2021. May be an image of text.

Photo by Positive & Motivational Quotes on July 27, 2021. May be an image of text that says '1. Figure Out Finances First If you're moving out for the first time, it can be difficult to figure out how to finance your new life. Rent should be no more than 30% of your income, or $750 or less, for example. Utility costs depend on where you're living, but may include water, electric, gas, internet, and phone. You'll need to budget for home furnishings, food, toiletries and transportation.'.
Photo by Positive & Motivational Quotes on July 27, 2021. May be an image of text.

Photo by Positive & Motivational Quotes on July 27, 2021. May be an image of text that says '3. Figure Out How to Do Basic Lifestyle Tasks Learn as much as you can about necessary home-focused tasks before moving out so that you can shorten the learning curve and get comfortable on your own much faster. This isn't to say you have to be a master at living on your own right off the bat-there's always the internet (and your parents) to refer to when you've got a question about how to do something. But do try to pick up whatever skills you can early on. You'll be glad you did.'.
Photo by Positive & Motivational Quotes on July 27, 2021. May be an image of text.

Photo by Positive & Motivational Quotes on July 27, 2021. May be an image of text that says '5. Figure Out Where You'll Need to Update Your Address As soon as you move to your new address you'll need to update the post office, as well as any companies that send you bills or other types of communications. If you moved to a different state, you'll need to get a new driver's license or I.D. card as well, and update your vehicle's registration if you brought a car along.'.
Photo by Positive & Motivational Quotes on July 27, 2021. May be an image of text that says 'I LOVE ALL TYPES OF PEOPLE, AS LONG AS THEY'RE SOLID. Sonya Teclai THE "OnO'.
